{"tid":877321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 工人清理山竹塌樹　遭塌下樹幹擊中昏迷","createTime":"2018-10-26T09:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T17:55:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e447165e124550db578a1f85d8d202c95d913868","tid":877321,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"屯門青山公路黃金海岸發生工業意外，今早(26日)10時許，一名姓羅（60歲）男工人，偕同工友在上址清理「山竹」過後倒塌的樹木。當羅正在鋸樹期間，一段長約3米、直徑約10厘米的樹幹突然塌下，羅猝不及防被擊中頭部，登時陷入昏迷，姓盧（22歲）女職員見有意外發生，即時報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181026/photo/bkn-20181026114210369-1026_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181026165228\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181026114210369-1026_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181026165228&h=7dcd738c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181026/bkn-20181026114210369-1026_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181026%2Fbkn-20181026114210369-1026_00822_001.html&d=pBvlUjHteML23fzRuHOJCsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=0db6e955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181026/bkn-20181026114210369-1026_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0d31191aa28eebb1cb81c5790345fcaaab57f3e1","tid":877321,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7747ba14839a12f86d9b5e36b488c278edef02d9","tid":877321,"uid":28076,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"依單又唔可以賴打完風唔停工既<br />\n啲樹始終都要執 啲工人安全意識有問題或者佢唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be0ee3b8ead7ab3e79c7a0a46a13bbb2d04f603","tid":877321,"uid":22360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"應該自己小心<br />\n<br />\n今次扣